text: Jaani is a romantic comedy Punjabi film starring Gippy Grewal and Navneet Kaur Dhillon. == Plot == It revolves around the love story of a taxi driver, played by Gippy, and a girl who has eloped from her home, played by Navneet. Supporting actors include Karamjit Anmol, BN Sharma, Anita Devgun and Seema Kaushal Release The film was shot in Fiji in June 2016 until 6 July 2016 and was expected to be released in October 2016. == Soundtrack == ==References== Category:Indian films Category:Films shot in Fiji Category:Indian romance films Category:Unreleased Indian films
title: Jaani (film)
